Docs.summary: Represents a runtime library dependency in a dependency manifest.

remarks.format:
## Remarks
A runtime library dependency is a library required to run an application. You can use the <xref:Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyModel.DependencyContext.RuntimeLibraries> property to get the list of runtime library dependencies for a dependency context. For an example, see <xref:Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyModel.DependencyContext> documentation.
